m`\n- Deserializes it with `ObjectInputStream`\n- Verifies entries are restored and the restored map remains mutable\n\nThis should reach the remaining `TrieMap.writeObject` and `TrieMap.readObject` dynamic-access call sites for Scala 2.11.8.\n\nI did not run compilation or tests locally, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0208a67830ac3785016a10443845f081a3b942c44fe2bd61d2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 446, "output": 459, "cacheRead": 33280, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34185, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779450930005, "responseId": "resp_0208a67830ac3785016a1044328e8881a38dcfe319f552e09e"}}
